<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THOUGHTS OF HEAVEN ARE SWEET</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Singcha gamlei ka sal tanna hi,
 Ka Pa'n A Cha thienglim mangin maw!
 Ei hung tanin, ei hung pui dawk tai,
 Ka kumtuong Pa chun.

[V2]
 Salem vangkhuo chuh,
 Lunghem lo a Aw!
 Hungtung thei din aw!
 Thagau ei puiin ka Pa kawmah.

[V3]
 2. Ka Lal ngul-ang A lupna tang chuh,
 Ka Pa'n A Cha pul A dona chuh;
 Keile do di'n Thagau ei puiin,
 Ka Lal thihna chuh.

[V4]
 3. Zie apat chun ka Pa In siem chuh,
 Lal thisan a zephawih nuom a chun;
 Hukdam haw leh Lal leh Pathien tawh,
 Kumkhuo'n leng ta'ng kau.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>364</hymn_number>
</song>